[30;1m371 | [0m[35mon the local disk customized with the `path` parameter. By default, the[0m
[30;1m372 | [0m[35msearched `index` is considered a query image, switch to the reference type by[0m
[30;1m373 | [0m[35menabling it with the `reference` parameter.[0m

[30;1m712 | [0m[35m``action`` and ``timeout`` arguments are new in SeleniumLibrary 3.0.[0m
[30;1m713 | [0m[35mIn earlier versions, the alert was always accepted and a timeout was[0m
[30;1m714 | [0m[35mhardcoded to one second.</doc>[0m
[30;1m715 | [0m[35m<shortdoc>Verifies that an alert is present and by default, accepts it.</shortdoc>[0m
[30;1m716 | [0m[35m</kw>[0m
